HEADWORD: Garrupa
<hw>Gar*ru"pa</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Prob. fr. Pg.
<ets>garupa</ets> crupper. Cf. <er>Grouper</er> the fish.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>One of several species of California market
fishes, of the genus <gen>Sebastichthys</gen>; -- called also
<altname>rockfish</altname>. See <er>Rockfish</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

